# Third Step

Complete chat (one server host a chat for multiple clients)

Model :
-------
                          ________
            -------> O___|        |
           |             | Client |
           |  ------- )__|        |
           | |           |________|
           | |     
 ________  | |            ________
|        |_( ------> O___|        |
| Server | | v           | Client |
|        |___O <----- )__|        |
|________| | ^           |________|
           | |                    
           | |            ________
            -------> O___|        |
             |           | Client |
              ------- )__|        |
                         |________|
             
Functions :
-----------

* From client to server :
    - inscription
    - diffusion

* From server to client :
    - printMsg

